Constraints:
    Players can not bid if they have full hand
    Players can not bid more spice than they have
        unless they are allied and their ally fronts
        the spice for purchase
    
    start with first player - position ahead of storm
    player choices: 
        - bid spice (amount < previous bid)
        - pass
    
    if all but one pass 
        - bid spice to emperor
        - card to playerHand
    
    Next round of bidding, unless no cards left
    Then NEXT PHASE